Index: linux-2.6.12-rc3-ckrm5/include/linux/ckrm_rc.h
===================================================================
--- /dev/null	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ linux-2.6.12-rc3-ckrm5/include/linux/ckrm_rc.h	2005-05-05 09:35:04.000000000 -0700
